{"tid":1722833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民賤聯議員落區清路障","createTime":"2019-11-15T04:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T05:33:44.000Z","uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"6c1a18c194df3775441fc7b5fe5c656464a723c0","tid":1722833,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:07:35.000Z","msg":"民建聯立法會議員葛珮帆今早在 Facebook 專頁說，清早和街坊在荃灣福來邨對開一起清理路障。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯昨早會見特首林鄭月娥，要求政府成立「止暴協調中心」及帶頭發起「全民止暴」，在警力不足之下，讓市民一同參與清理路障及連儂牆等工作。<br />\n<br />\n主席李慧琼說，由於警力不足，要求特首帶領問責團隊發動全民參與止暴運動，例如清理路障、連儂牆等工作，「好多市民其實都好想參與，所以我們要求政府想辦法，帶頭在安全合法的途徑下讓市民參與。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NYfCeiE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNYfCeiE.jpg&h=7f35a974&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8fe1b2e9b7ea12e9d790f5be683f893a61a1c9e3","tid":1722833,"uid":301820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:10:19.000Z","msg":"準備大垃圾桶清垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a938555ff8004ee9ccb767f286deb8a4cc4dc85","tid":1722833,"uid":137316,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:12:20.000Z","msg":"白衫暴徒麥美娟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0532770ce575ee98f06535ebe71b0aae26f6c6c","tid":1722833,"uid":108560,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:12:40.000Z","msg":"執完兩舊收工 做show<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f60681d91d95d61a3f5e9d87f843a0c76e39bed","tid":1722833,"uid":90601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:13:04.000Z","msg":"麥美娟條撚屌 尋日青衣tg放題 你去撚左邊?"},{"pid":"e60abacebe7022228bd1f59b0fd89e9eb122be85","tid":1722833,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T04:13:46.000Z","msg":"選舉近了"},{"pid":"0cafbc5c7013eefd4